This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and question answering. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to NLP. Additionally, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) could also be possible sub-categories as they involve techniques used in this paper such as ensembling and neural networks.
